    Glass Type 1,            !- Name
    SpectralAverage,         !- Optical Data Type
    ,                        !- Window Glass Spectral Data Set Name
    0.003048,                !- Thickness {m}
    0.834,                   !- Solar Transmittance at Normal Incidence
